Close Duplicate Tabs is a handy Chrome extension that allows you to easily close duplicate tabs in your browser, freeing up space and improving your browsing efficiency. With just a few clicks, you can close all tabs that contain the same website, keeping only one tab open. This extension is perfect for anyone who frequently opens multiple tabs to the same webpage, or who wants to streamline their browsing experience.

If you're looking for a way to tidy up your browser and speed up your browsing, make sure to try out Close Duplicate Tabs today.
